    "improvements_made": "Added explicit lookup tables for all status fields (DEVICE_STATUS, TRAFFIC_STATUS, CONNECTION_STATUS, FAILURE_HANDLE_STATUS) to enforce consistent enumerations. Introduced a many‑to‑many relationship between STAFF and FAILURE via the associative entity FAILURE_ASSIGNMENT, allowing multiple technicians per failure and capturing assignment details. Included created_at and updated_at timestamps on every entity for audit trails. Updated attribute names for consistency and replaced generic status attributes with foreign keys to the new status lookup tables. Ensured all core concepts remain and relationships are clearly defined."
